）曾出席在台北舉行的「撐香港，要自由音樂會」，他上台力撐港人抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指林夕超過3千首的填詞作品，被內地音樂網封殺及下架，有網民翻查內地音樂網，如「酷狗」或「QQ音樂」等網站，在欄目輸入林夕個名後，均會出現「沒有搜尋到相關歌曲」，或者輸入林夕填詞的歌名後，會顯示「很抱歉，你查看的歌曲已下架」等字眼，當中就連林夕曾為北京奧運填詞的《北京歡迎你》，也未能搜尋到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港樂可唔可以復活睇呢次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba6cdb84a4724e8c114eaff8852399e335edb4e","tid":1746000,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"王菲冇歌唱<br />\n九成歌都係林夕作詞<br />\n即係封殺埋王菲，演唱會都冇得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb783b70c61bc50b4208941f00b4807ad7921df2","tid":1746000,"uid":286210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"到時咪唱返啲山歌囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074e568472103bac806bfe545587a5355835e84e","tid":1746000,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d32fb1ccafa4c39c5fff76287218fdfa8fab05a","tid":1746000,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"我唸下先.<br />\n四大天王.黎明.張學友.王菲.楊千華.容祖兒.eason.呢堆咪無歌唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差唔多成個港樂要收晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"eason大把國語"}]}